casebody.data:
No. 71,

Misc.

Ex parte Cogdell et al.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus granted. A *806rule is ordered.to issue, returnable within thirty days, requiring the respondents to show cause why the petition for writ of mandamus should not be granted.

George E. C. Hayes, James M. Nabrit, Jr. and George M. Johnson for petitioners. Vernon E. West, Chester H. Gray and Milton H. Korman for McGuire et al., respondents.
